# Knowledge Shorts Production Pipeline - Environment Variables

# OpenAI API Key (required if using OpenAI TTS)
# Get your key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key-here

# ElevenLabs API Key (optional, alternative TTS provider)
# Get your key from: https://elevenlabs.io
# ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=your-elevenlabs-api-key-here

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Replace the placeholder values with your actual API keys
# 3. Never commit .env to version control (it's in .gitignore)

# Alternative: Use free Google TTS
# No API key needed - just change tts_provider in settings.yaml to "gtts"
